content: Hi! So I am hosting a virtual phone bank and submitted a request for a training facilitator and a tech captain volunteer on the google form. I havenâ€™t heard back yet, but the dates of my planned phone bank have changed and I was wondering how to proceed with re-requesting. Thanks!

Hi, <@1276014775444443136>! To be a facilitator you need to go through training. I believe <@791857656897732648> has linked to the trainings below if you are interested in joining!

Our VOTE team has 3 distinct positions, including Facilitator. To train to be a part of our VOTE team, refer to this document: https://docs.google.com/document/d/1WfH8QHMgx-bFDLojWoJOtuMmx5tu2AOPZo-FMP0Aoig/edit#heading=h.sg8e2cha55q3
This doc and more info is located here: https://discord.com/channels/1242249109298221066/1270926045499101338

Thank you, <@965992907981074443>! The question on training came up after, but the opening poster has a question on submitting a date change for a phone bank they are hosting and have asked for some Vote team folks to help with. Could you take a look at the top of this thread and see if you can help?
<@1257469301435400238> was saying she'd look into it for them. I think that's our best course of action. What are the dates for the change? I think that will help Frances planning-wise.

The "tiny window" will open if you click on it.
